display_startup_experience: Biznes təcrübəniz haqqında məlumat (STARTUP) Xüsusilə böyük yaş qrupunda olan komandalar üçün hakimlər biznes və sahibkarlıq (STARTUP) aspektləri ilə bağlı daha çox suallar verirlər. Zəhmət olmasa,  bu sahədə müvafiq təcrübəniz  varsa qeyd edin. Bu, baş hakimlərimiz tərəfindən hakim qruplarını hazırlamaq üçün yaxşı məlumatdır.

about_title_3: WRO® operates on, is measured on and strives towards the following Values:
about_diversity: WRO is accessible to young people from around the world, regardless of background
about_teamwork: Our teams succeed by embracing collaboration and build friendships
about_passion: Learning occurs naturally when participants are in flow and having fun when engaged in our activities
about_innovation: Our programs are innovative and hands-on, based around trending topics and technologies
olympics_body_1: In 2023 teams will learn about shipping logistics and about the infrastructure for our digital technology. They will investigate how robots can help both shipping and digital technology infrastructure to be more safe, more sustainable and more efficient.
olympics_body_2: Be aware that in your country local competitions may follow slightly different rules. Always use the rules your National Organizer provides. Please contact your National Organizer first when you have questions relating to the games & rules. Click on the button to find your National Organizer.
